{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2040, "height": 2713, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "窑湾", "block_bbox": [1000, 222, 1219, 289], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "仁村乡北坻坞村，位于县城东北，距县城20公里，有139户，9620口人，1556亩耕地。窑湾是北坻坞村的一个小组，处于北坻坞村的南端，杜氏宗祠的西侧，有160余口人（迁出的不算）。杜氏自明初由晋迁绳时家传有诗圣杜甫牌一尊。明万历年间，杜氏被敕封为义民后建祠，将杜甫牌位移人祠内供奉，并将祠西之地命名为窑湾，杜氏长门迁此居住，以示纪念诗圣。\n", "block_bbox": [367, 357, 1856, 670], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [204, 706, 282, 1404], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "\\fra ", "block_bbox": [216, 2050, 269, 2136], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "窑湾杜氏始祖为渑池杜氏五世祖三光世系：", "block_bbox": [458, 688, 1227, 734], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——忠—果——真金——三光(—派)——从龙腾龙", "block_bbox": [458, 750, 1464, 865], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "祖莹在上西村西坡组大块地（七世祖璋所配李氏亦葬于此），后分卜葬老蛇沟、岭南、北坑塔。\n", "block_bbox": [371, 885, 1853, 1000], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8984254002571106, "coordinate": [367.3238525390625, 357.60052490234375, 1856.2535400390625, 670.7468872070312]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8719016909599304, "coordinate": [371.88922119140625, 885.7200927734375, 1853.4326171875, 1000.5546875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.747136116027832, "coordinate": [458.130645751